  "title": "New Bottle, Still Old Wine? China, Social Change, and Sociology",
  "abstract": "In this article I describe the recent trends in sociological research in China and the sociological study of China in the West. I discuss how sociologists can learn from each other in the study of economic and social changes taking place in China and contribute to general knowledge in the discipline of sociology.",
